{"tid":139090,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"陽光超兇妹「露深溝吃螃蟹」網友看呆：身材真是Holy蟹！","createTime":"2017-03-01T06:37:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-04T06:43:46.000Z","uid":9573,"like":91,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"223d3aa5dc01eb991dff22598f1d8d35f054ba05","tid":139090,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T06:37:25.000Z","msg":"大家都愛看存在世界上美好的事物，若有幸碰上身材穠纖合度、擁有「人間胸器」的大正妹，更不免讓人多看幾眼。就有網友使用社交軟體Instagram時，無意間找到一位自稱「陽光」的女孩，只見相簿中充滿熱情奔放、享受生活的自然美照，尤其一張「深溝吃螃蟹」，讓無數人看呆了。<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2363/d2363288.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2363%2Fd2363288.jpg&h=c65cb837&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2363/2363287.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2363%2F2363287.jpg&h=53a34392&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲正如她的IG帳號，滿滿的陽光和大自然風情！<br />\n<br />\n「陽光妹」來自菲律賓宿霧，IG上有高達7萬6千人追蹤，在當地頗有名氣，常分享生活美照，更不吝嗇展現「兇狠」好身材。她寫道，最愛的4件事分別是旅行世界、時尚、美食和自然，和大量照片中陽光、沙灘、比基尼的風格相當符合，且不管是美豔性感或時尚典雅都能切換自如，完全藏不住迷人身材！<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2363/2363285.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2363%2F2363285.jpg&h=118644ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲美食和美人，人間絕配。<br />\n<br />\n其中「吃螃蟹照」更引來網友關注，只見「陽光妹」一段影片中，她穿著清涼、獨自面對一大盆活體螃蟹，再把它們一隻一隻移到洗手槽中，為烹調做準備。接著的照片，只見她拿著一杯紅酒，面對如山高的螃蟹堆，讓人食指大動，更露出深不見底的事業線，美食配美人，人間最美風景。<br />\n<br />\n照片分享出來，吸引許多網友熱烈討論，多數人驚嘆實在太正身材又好，不過也有些人懷疑修圖加分很大，「好大......我是說螃蟹」、「菲律賓有很多混血兒」、「重點是胸部吧」、「我這個人很單純，推了」「還是朱千雪比夠合眼緣」、「用美肌程式吧」、「正到像假人」、「身材太扯了」、「最好你會穿這樣去健身」。<br />\n<br />\n▼健身。<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2363/2363295.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2363%2F2363295.jpg&h=06fd50ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▼愛狗。<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2363/2363293.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2363%2F2363293.jpg&h=c092592b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▼刷牙。<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2363/2363291.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2363%2F2363291.jpg&h=82b75e56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▼時尚。<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2363/2363294.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2363%2F2363294.jpg&h=ca575032&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▼梁國雄。<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2012/03/1203191703462120.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2012%2F03%2F1203191703462120.jpg&h=51cfae09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▼鮮花。<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2363/2363289.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2363%2F2363289.jpg&h=462951a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▼度假。<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2363/2363286.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2363%2F2363286.jpg&h=9f09430c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a4fa191913efbbbfa4756bad2fbab6c93194a57a","tid":139090,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T06:38:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"972d632791c3a5f9ffb7232a64c0a37c4b08c4e3","tid":139090,"uid":42469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T06:39:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n梁國雄都J <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9b39f95880fd8cf201b9262e456548c57703e2b","tid":139090,"uid":54704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T06:40:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/